# Declarative label set consumed by seed-github.sh (create-or-update; never deletes).
# Each entry: name (the label, which carries the meaning on its own — never rely on color alone),
# color (6-digit hex, no leading '#'), description (what the label asserts).
# Edit here and re-run the seed script to reconcile labels in the repo.

- name: priority:high
  color: b60205
  description: Pick this up before lower-priority work.
- name: priority:med
  color: d93f0b
  description: Normal priority; schedule after high-priority items.
- name: priority:low
  color: fbca04
  description: Nice to have; do when capacity allows.

- name: size:s
  color: c2e0c6
  description: Small effort estimate (hours).
- name: size:m
  color: 7ac142
  description: Medium effort estimate (a day or a few).
- name: size:l
  color: 1d7637
  description: Large effort estimate (multiple days); consider breaking into sub-issues.

- name: level:L0
  color: ededed
  description: Belongs to escalation level L0 (sane repo skeleton).
- name: level:L1
  color: d4d4f5
  description: Belongs to escalation level L1.
- name: level:L2
  color: b8b8ef
  description: Belongs to escalation level L2 (reproducible pipeline).
- name: level:L3
  color: 9c9ce8
  description: Belongs to escalation level L3 (collaboration and governance).
- name: level:L4
  color: 7e7ee0
  description: Belongs to escalation level L4.
- name: level:L5
  color: 5a5ad6
  description: Belongs to escalation level L5 (governed, FAIR, published OKF bundle).

- name: type:data
  color: 0e8a16
  description: A data-quality problem or known dataset limitation.
- name: type:docs
  color: 1d76db
  description: Documentation, data dictionary, or narrative work.
- name: type:pipeline
  color: 5319e7
  description: The reproducible pipeline, scripts, or modules under src/.
- name: type:governance
  color: b60205
  description: Roles, access tiers, charter, responsible-data, or ethics work.
- name: type:infra
  color: 333333
  description: Environment, CI, tooling, or repository plumbing.

- name: blocking
  color: e11d21
  description: Gates other work or a guarded action; resolve before that action or before climbing a level.
- name: good-first-issue
  color: 7057ff
  description: Well-scoped and approachable for a new contributor.
- name: help-wanted
  color: 008672
  description: Maintainers are actively seeking help on this.
